	<p> I would love to visit Glacier National Park because of the outdoor activities, wildlife, park drives, iconic features, geological sites, and its suitability for camping. The historic and architectual wonder and the majestic nature of The Royal Palace including its limestone statues makes it worth visiting.</p>
